&lt;p&gt;This is with the TCM patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17791682" author="krummas" created="Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:28:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/krummas/cassandra/commit/f395c60bc73e89714f31c741b51953e07ff93ce1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/krummas/cassandra/commit/f395c60bc73e89714f31c741b51953e07ff93ce1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the reason is a race between creating the MV while we have ongoing writes - the MV is first added to TableViews before the schema is activated by committing the transformation. Patch just checks the cluster metadata if the MV is in the schema before it starts taking writes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ci coming soon&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
